<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_223_r1l6">Franckfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_223_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> <expan>Bu<ex>r</ex>khart</expan> peſler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvie 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Er </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_223_r1l8">Jm hans <expan>Troſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> der auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> iſt vnd ſein purgrecht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_223_r1l9">vor vns noch nÿe <expan>aufgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / ſein habe bey euch mit dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_223_r1l10"><expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> bekümert hab . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Burkhart </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_223_r1l12">peſler darynne 
<add><ab facs="#facs_223_r1l11"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> cʒum <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>fürderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd beholffen ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_223_r1l13">wöllet / Als etc Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_223" id="111v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Franckfurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan>Bu<ex>r</ex>khart</expan> Pesler, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie im Hans
                            <expan>Trosp<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> der auch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ist und sein purgrecht vor uns noch nye
                                <expan>aufgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, sein habe bey euch mit dem
                                <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> bekümert hab.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Burkhart Pesler darynne
                                    <add><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> czum
                            <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und beholffen sein wöllet, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
